      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"6. REGAL SAINT has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and two placings from seven starts. Scored by 2.5 lengths last time (19.66) in a Grade 5 over 352m at Q Lakeside. Looks the one to beat with even luck. 2. LOST YOUR MARKER was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 3.5 lengths win at this track in a handy 18.75. Fair draw can see a good run and goes well at this distance. One of the prime contenders. 1. MAJESTIC ETHICS put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Velocity Yin (16.97) in a P5. Expecting another good run. 3. LITTLE ROWDY hit the frame latest (19.14) when third at this track in a Grade 5. Already a winner from this draw.\",\"runners\":[6,2,1,3],\"exclusive\":false}",
